	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001026_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>57 Sloane St.</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">23<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">d</hi></hi> May</p>
<lb/><p rend="right">1857</p>
<lb/><p><persName>Sir George Back</persName></p>
<lb/><p>We never 
<lb/>did ourselves the 
<lb/>honour of returning 
<lb/>the kind call 
<lb/>of <persName>Lady Back</persName>
<lb/>because we 
<lb/>have been so 
<lb/>closely occupied 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001026_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'--> 
<lb/>with the narrative. 
<lb/>And we are now 
<lb/>about to go out 
<lb/>a little way into 
<lb/>the country for 
<lb/>the sake of quiet 
<lb/>in order thereby 
<lb/>to finish the 
<lb/>same work. We 
<lb/>think of Barnet 
<lb/>and will leave 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001026_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'--> 
<lb/>on Tuesday next<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I hope <persName>Lady Back</persName> will excuse my 
<lb/>want of politeness<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>A gospel 
<lb/>according to Luke 
<lb/>came to me this 
<lb/>morning probably 
<lb/>in Esquimo, 
<lb/>the address is not 
<lb/>in your hand 
<lb/>and no note 
<lb/>accompanied it 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001026_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'--> 
<lb/>I hope people don<reg>'</reg>t 
<lb/>think I need <hi rend="underline">cooling</hi>
<lb/>in your cold 
<lb/>regions, for I 
<lb/>think you have 
<lb/>done quite enough 
<lb/>there and the very 
<lb/>thought of your 
<lb/>ice-bergs makes 
<lb/>me shiver. Did 
<lb/>you try your 
<lb/>hand at <placeName>the Falls</placeName><reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>I am &amp;c most truly 
<lb/>yours</p>
<lb/><p>D. Livingstone</p><addSpan spanTo="#p.1r-01" place="marginleft"><!--addSpan/@place='left margin of fol. 1r'--></addSpan>
<lb/><p>Please do not trouble yourself to 
<lb/>answer this. I mean only <placeName>the Falls</placeName> are very difficult<reg>.</reg></p><anchor xml:id="p.1r-01"/>
			
</div>
